Title: Prisoner Preservation
Description:
The beasts took our people! Dragged them away when we were gettin' our first rest since our escape!

We only just escaped those nerubians. We can't afford ta lose more people.

Search Pillar-nest Vosh. It's where all those beasts came from. If we're lucky our people are still alive.
CompletionText: Survivin' ain't easy, but we gotta keep pushin' on.
RewardText: You did all you could. I be in your debt. We be honorin' Jeti's memory by dealing with da nest.
